<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_415_r1l29"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Matheis / Als wir ew vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Gorge<ex>n</ex></expan> vom liehtenſtein 
<add><ab facs="#facs_415_r1l28"><expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>vett<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab></add> vnd auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_415_r1l31"><expan>Eberh<ex>art</ex></expan> fuchſen vormals cʒu einander <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von Jütten 
<add><ab facs="#facs_415_r1l30">Mayerin </ab></add> der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_415_r1l32">Judin wegen / als dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> burgerin vvorden iſt / 
<del rend="strikethrough">Alſo bit </del> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_415_r1l33"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief vnd <expan>Antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> darümb wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> / vnd wir bıten <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_415_r1l34">
<del rend="strikethrough">vv </del> mit <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiſʒ daʒ Jr durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vville<ex>n</ex></expan> mitſampt <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_415_r1l35"><expan>freunde<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> hılff vnd <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> darcʒu tun vvöllet / daʒ <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Judin </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_415_r1l36"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> burgerin Jr gelt vnd habe dıe Jr <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> iſt worden wider vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_415_r1l37">auch der knab Jr kind der <expan>gefange<ex>n</ex></expan> iſt ledig werde Als etc das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_415_r1l38"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>r</ex>ıa</expan> vj̃ <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> valentinı </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_415" id="207r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Matheis vom Liehtenstein </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Matheis, als wir ew und
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Gorge<ex>n</ex></expan> vom Liehtenstein,
                                                  <add><expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>vett<ex>er</ex>n</expan></add>, und auch
                                                  <expan>Eberh<ex>art</ex></expan> Fuchsen vormals
                                                czu einander
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von Jütten
                                                  <add>Mayerin</add>, der judin, wegen, als die
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burgerin worden ist,
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief und
                                                  <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> darümb wol
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>; und wir biten
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit
                                                  <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz, daz ir
                                                durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> mitsampt
                                                  <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>freunde<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> hilff und
                                                  <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> darczu tun
                                                wöllet, daz <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Judin,
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> burgerin, ir gelt
                                                und habe, die ir <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> ist
                                                worden, wider und auch der knab, ir kind, der
                                                  <expan>gefange<ex>n</ex></expan> ist, ledig werde.
                                                Als etc. Das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>r</ex>ia</expan> vi
                                                  <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Valentini.</ab>
</div>
